content.description: Climb the start for Quiche.  Take the upper crack to the left up to a natural belay stance.  The upper section has 2 bolts.  Often climbed in 2 pitches.
content.protection: Gear and bolts.  4th class scramble up to the Jolly anchor.
content.location: Same as Quiche, same cove as Poodle.

content.description: Climb the opening moves at 5.7 up into easier climbing above.
content.protection: Small stoppers, plus typical trad rack
content.location: Same area as Poodle.  Use Jolly Rover rap station, 2 ropes or 2 raps.

content.description: Climb up through two bolts and trend left into the finger crack.  Work up below the rap station to a big bucket up top.
content.protection: 2 bolts and gear, rap station (2 rope) 150'
content.location: Start right of Buffalo Stance, in a corner, same start as Poodle Bait.

content.description: Good climbing the pro and footing can get a little thin about half way up.  A fun line to climb with a spectacular view.
content.location: Scramble across to the left up near the cave and on the other side behind a big boulder is the start.  Climbs the ramp up and left across to the shoulder directly across from moon wall.  Rap off a single bolt (yikes), take a sling as backup if the one there is old.

content.description: Climb up the gully to a horn type formation.  A few bolts protect the upper section up to a 2 bolt anchor.  Easy terrain for the exit left.
content.protection: Trad rack and bolts, 2 bolt anchor.
content.location: Start at the bottom of the hole.

content.description: Climb the chimney up into a thin crack, then onto an easier face to clip the bolt
content.protection: Trad rack with thin TCU's, 1 bolt.
content.location: Start below the house sized boulder.

content.description: Climb from the deep hole up past 4 bolts.  Run out is over easy terrain.  2 cruxes at 1st and after the 4th
content.location: Start in the big hole right of Poodle and Quiche.  Use Jolly Rover rap station, 2 ropes or 2 raps.

content.description: Climb the face right of Poodle.  Climb past 2 bolts up to a good pocket.  Friction moves up to a slight overhang (5.7)
content.protection: 2 bolts, gear for the pocket, Rap off Poodle Station
content.location: Right of Poodle, same starting area.

content.description: Climbs the face just right of Jolly all the way up to the mid anchor.
Climb the weird corner to the left of Poodle Pounder. Kinda runout and poor rock. About 50 feet up take a ramp up and left along a big crack.
content.protection: Nuts and cams from 0.3 to 3.5 inches
content.location: Corner left of Poodle Pounder.  Rap off the Poodle Pounder bolt and sling.

content.description: Some moderate trad lines from a 5.6 up to a 10c.
